-- Packages do not contain duplicate package sections. No bug SC0002.

PACKAGE pack3
PUBLIC 

  THREAD myThr

  END myThr;

  
PRIVATE

  THREAD myThr2

  END myThr2;


END pack3;

-- public & private sections of the package are declared in two separate package declarations

PRIVATE

  THREAD myThr3

  END myThr3;


END pack4;

PACKAGE pack4
